   .. group-tab:: GPIO

      Operate with the test LED :hwftlbl-led:`L5` at :rpi-pico-pio:`GP21`:

      .. container:: highlight highlight-console notranslate

         .. parsed-literal::

            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio get gpio0 21**
            0

            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio conf gpio0 21 oh0**
            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio set gpio0 21 1**
            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio set gpio0 21 0**

            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio blink gpio0 21**
            Hit any key to exit

      Operate with the ENTER test key :hwftlbl-btn:`K2` at :rpi-pico-pio:`GP13`:

      .. container:: highlight highlight-console notranslate

         .. parsed-literal::

            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio get gpio0 13**
            0

            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio conf gpio0 13 iul**
            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio get gpio0 13**
            0
            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio get gpio0 13**
            1
            :bgn:`uart:~$` **gpio get gpio0 13**
            0

